<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Nur</author>
<title>Bárin de bilesiń Qudaıym meniń</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Saǵan teńdeı nurly ándetemiz,
 Sharyqtaıdy ánde túnekte Ózińe.
 Senen jasyra almaı men eshteńeni,
 Bárinde kóresiń, bárinde sezesiń,
 Bárinde bilesiń Qudaıym meniń.

[C1]
   Keremet ǵajap jasaǵan isteriń,
   Muny men shyn júrekten moıyndaımyn.
   Seni maqtaımyn, tamasha jaraldym,
   Muny men shyn júrekten moıyndaımyn.
   Na-na-na-na-na

[V2]
 Seniń bar oılaryń maǵan joǵary,
 Aqylyńda qanshama olardyń sany.
 Sanap shyqsam barlyq oı josparyńdy,
 Ǵylym sany jetpeıdi, oıymnan ketpeıdi,
 Keremet isteriń Qudaıym meniń.</lyrics>
</song>